quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  25,33,"Ne shibalakhurerera okhuchelasia khwosikhwosi tawe halali khwitsa okhukhwishilia obwatoto nende okhukhurerera obukalukhasi obulayi."
  25,34,"Balia balikhung’asibwa mafumama nibayilwa mumulilo, abo baliba habundu habii nende abakora muno injila."
  25,35,"Ne toto khwahelesia Musa Eshitabu, ne nikhumuwa halala ninaye Omusiani wabu Haruni okhuba omukhoonyi wuwe."
  25,36,"Nikhubaboolela mbu: “Tsie khubandu abakatsula ebimanyisio biefu.” Mana nikhubasishia okhusishia khwene."
  25,37,"Ne Abandu ba Nuhu, olwa bakatsula Abarumwa, khwabasishia mumatsi, nikhubakhola okhuba eshimanyisio khubandu, ne khwarecheshela abamabii eshinyasio eshilulu."
  25,38,"Nende A’d, nende Thamud, nende Abandu ba Ra’s (bolukoba) nende tsinzibulo tsindi tsinyinji etsiali hakari wabu."
  25,39,"Ne boosi khwabachelasilia, ne boosi khwabasishia busishia."
  25,40,"Ne toto bano boola khulukongo olweshilibwa ifula imbii mana kho koo, shibalikhwo nibalulolanga tawe, halali bo shibasuubilanga okhulamusibwa tawe."
  25,41,"Ne nibakhulola, bakhukholelanga omubayo, “Koo, uno niye owa Nyasaye yaruma abe omurumwa?"
  25,42,"Toto ye yali ahambi muno okhukhukosia efwe ehale nende abanyasaye befu, khukhayanga okhwisumilisia khubo.” Ahambi hano betsa okhumanya nibalola eshimanyisio mbu ni wina owakora muno injila."
  25,43,"Koo, walolakhwo ulia wakhola obwikombi bubwe okhuba Nyasaye wuwe? Kho koo, ewe wakhaba omuhabini wuwe?"